{"tid":1128301,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"淘仔耳機集中討論(37) - 買返去慢慢試","createTime":"2019-04-27T17:25:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T17:35:46.000Z","uid":6460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"231754f167f6b9f254a33ddb1bbe5b8c50ea8691","tid":1128301,"uid":6460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T17:25:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www4.hiendy.com/hififorum/data/attachment/forum/201608/08/164641yntgpqd6t6nprtpn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww4.hiendy.com%2Fhififorum%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F201608%2F08%2F164641yntgpqd6t6nprtpn.jpg&h=47e9529d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">新嚟嘅巴打可以先睇睇FAQ、常用簡稱，咁就可以快啲知道我地傾緊乜:</span></strong><br />\n(例：日馬= 日本Amazon，唔係沙田賽馬早場&hellip;)<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/2rRR54\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F2rRR54&d=VPc2G2a59adbLf1ajQMU8l8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=057913c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/2rRR54</a><br />\n<br />\n近期熱門推介列表 / 其他淘寶店鋪 (Member Only):<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n高登/連登巴打耳機包膠集:<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/BXWSv3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FBXWSv3&d=VPc2G2a59adbLf1ajQMU8l8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=0ecfdcb5\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/BXWSv3</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就黎1001/差唔多1個月沉底搵人搵過個新POST<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/ZQUicP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FZQUicP&d=VPc2G2a59adbLf1ajQMU8l8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=1a3dd850\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/ZQUicP</a><br />\n<br />\n***重要聲明***<br />\n<br />\n1. 淘仔野有時可能會非常超值。但產品價格可升可跌，甚至變成毫無2手價。 <br />\n2. 買淘仔野未必一定能夠穩賺性價比，人地買到果把聲未必等於你聽到果把，耳機做功同聽感冇一定既保證，因為大多數冇QC就出貨， <br />\n3. 購買淘仔耳機可能會招致損失&mdash;&gt;寄返大陸走黎走去都係時間同錢。<br />\n___________________________________________________________________<br />\n<br />\n舊帖內有以下既耳機討論<br />\n<br />\n悅耳 :1圈4鐵,6單 <br />\n美樂城seek keep: diy se535 vs2 <br />\n聲菲爾音頻商城 : diy K3003 <br />\n值得逛逛 : diy 535四單終極調音版動鐵版<br />\n線材 小凡/發燒銀線坊<br />\n<br />\n舊Post合集<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1pxY3M-1E0cpWfXhUhzqoo-Yiv2xIySlf8not4FcEcnQ/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1pxY3M-1E0cpWfXhUhzqoo-Yiv2xIySlf8not4FcEcnQ%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=VPc2G2a59adbLf1ajQMU8l8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=c3909dd8\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1pxY3M-1E0cpWfXhUhzqoo-Yiv2xIySlf8not4FcEcnQ/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n開Post格式<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/ZQUicP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FZQUicP&d=VPc2G2a59adbLf1ajQMU8l8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=1a3dd850\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/ZQUicP</a><br />\n<br />\n使用器材列表<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1jwkKF3PE7SYRu5nbYMCdCOKkyKnwErYamydXRDUrdos/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1jwkKF3PE7SYRu5nbYMCdCOKkyKnwErYamydXRDUrdos%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=VPc2G2a59adbLf1ajQMU8l8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=c5d08d30\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1jwkKF3PE7SYRu5nbYMCdCOKkyKnwErYamydXRDUrdos/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dbd655adbc1038db4296108cf0c79a22e0bf07e","tid":1128301,"uid":6460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T17:25:42.000Z","msg":"頂 咁都中伏 諗住留比下個人中架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7437b64123c496f091d41db1118b5f60c53e940","tid":1128301,"uid":94419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T17:27:45.0